# Code
```java []
class Solution {
    public int candy(int[] rating) {
        int n=rating.length;
        int[] res=new int[n];
        Arrays.fill(res,1);
        
        for(int i=1; i<n; i++){
            if(rating[i]>rating[i-1]){
                res[i] += res[i-1];
            }
        }
        for(int i=n-2; i>=0; i--){

            if(rating[i] > rating[i+1]){
                res[i] += res[i+1];
            }
        }
        for(int i=1; i<n-1; i++){
            if (res[i] - Math.max(res[i-1], res[i+1]) > 1){
                res[i] = Math.max(res[i-1], res[i+1]) + 1;
            }
        }
        return Arrays.stream(res).sum();
    }
}
```

